Language: en

00:00:01.040 --> 00:00:05.900
I recommend to cook a potato sticks with cheese 

00:00:05.900 --> 00:00:10.239
for those who wish to diversify their diet and try the new version of cooking potatoes.

00:00:10.239 --> 00:00:12.469
For this recipe we need:

00:00:12.469 --> 00:00:18.079
7 small potatoes, 100 g of hard cheese, 2 eggs, 100-150 g of bread crumbs, 3 tbsp of flour,

00:00:18.079 --> 00:00:26.980
spices: black pepper, coriander, turmeric, salt and olive oil for frying.

00:00:26.980 --> 00:00:29.020
Let's start cooking.

00:00:29.020 --> 00:00:34.770
I have prepared a double boiler with hot water.

00:00:34.770 --> 00:00:41.750
Put a potato here. Will boil it on steam.

00:00:41.750 --> 00:00:47.220
Potatoes can be boiled in their skins and in the usual way.

00:00:47.220 --> 00:00:49.360
Cover with a lid.

00:00:49.360 --> 00:00:54.000
Turn on medium heat and cook.

00:00:54.300 --> 00:00:58.600
Who cooks the potatoes in water, checks its readiness using a fork.

00:00:58.600 --> 00:01:03.989
I am guided by thermocontroller: when the arrow reaches the end of a green sector - I will turn off the heat.

00:01:03.989 --> 00:01:08.500
Leave for 15 minutes with the lid closed.

00:01:08.800 --> 00:01:10.149
It took 15 minutes.

00:01:10.149 --> 00:01:12.630
I opened the lid.

00:01:12.630 --> 00:01:18.440
Check the potatoes. It is well pierced with a fork.

00:01:18.440 --> 00:01:23.200
Leave it to cool slightly.

00:01:23.600 --> 00:01:30.400
Grate fine cooled and peeled potatoes.

00:01:30.890 --> 00:01:37.280
In grated potatoes add spices to taste.

00:01:37.280 --> 00:01:41.050
Turmeric.

00:01:41.050 --> 00:01:44.740
Add a little coriander.

00:01:44.740 --> 00:01:47.940
A little black pepper.

00:01:47.940 --> 00:01:50.830
All this is to your liking.

00:01:50.830 --> 00:01:57.830
Be sure to salt.

00:01:57.830 --> 00:02:00.970
Then try and add more if necessary.

00:02:00.970 --> 00:02:07.970
Two eggs.

00:02:09.949 --> 00:02:15.000
Stir.

00:02:16.059 --> 00:02:21.399
Turmeric gave potatoes a nice sunny color.

00:02:21.399 --> 00:02:23.079
Yellow.

00:02:23.079 --> 00:02:31.259
Add 3 tablespoons of flour.

00:02:31.259 --> 00:02:37.959
Making potato dough.

00:02:37.959 --> 00:02:42.000
Again mix well.

00:02:42.719 --> 00:02:45.600
We are kneading a potato dough.

00:02:45.600 --> 00:02:48.489
It is sticky and viscous.

00:02:48.489 --> 00:02:51.609
Set grill to warm up.

00:02:51.609 --> 00:02:58.319
Pour refined olive oil.

00:02:58.319 --> 00:03:00.999
A little.

00:03:00.999 --> 00:03:03.000
Let warming up.

00:03:03.000 --> 00:03:09.600
Pour a little oil in a separate bowl.

00:03:13.400 --> 00:03:18.879
Cheese should be cut into small wedges.

00:03:18.879 --> 00:03:22.000
Cut lengthwise.

00:03:22.000 --> 00:03:29.100
Cut into small wedges.

00:03:32.639 --> 00:03:39.599
Smear your hands with vegetable oil.

00:03:39.599 --> 00:03:43.679
Will form the potato patties.

00:03:43.679 --> 00:03:47.439
Smear the hands with oil so the dough will not stick to hands.

00:03:47.439 --> 00:03:51.589
Do a pankacke.

00:03:51.589 --> 00:03:54.649
Put cheese into it.

00:03:54.649 --> 00:04:00.229
Close up.

00:04:00.229 --> 00:04:07.259
Form the sticks.

00:04:07.259 --> 00:04:16.859
Bread all sides around.

00:04:16.859 --> 00:04:20.329
Put on a grill.

00:04:20.329 --> 00:04:25.500
Fry all four sides, turning.

00:04:26.069 --> 00:04:30.520
Fry over medium heat.

00:04:30.520 --> 00:04:35.419
Once they were fried on one side, turn over to the other.

00:04:35.419 --> 00:04:42.419
Then fry laterally.

00:04:44.400 --> 00:04:48.159
Potato sticks with cheese can be a separate dish.

00:04:48.159 --> 00:04:51.700
Also, they can be served as a garnish for fish and meat.

00:04:51.700 --> 00:04:56.800
Cook with pleasure and enjoy!

